title: Ep 6 | The Return to the Trump Hotel, Phil's Underwear Standoff, and the Fall of Man
description:
Jase returns to the Trump Hotel after his awkward encounter with hotel security, Phil tells about the time he had a standoff in his underwear, and the question is asked: Whose fault was the fall of man, Adam's or Eve's?
